FBIS3-19200 "drweu049_a_94004" FBIS-WEU-94-049 Document Type:Daily Report 14 Mar 1994 AUSTRIA Ex-GDR Minister Confirms Existence of Stasi Spies AU1303162694 Vienna KURIER in German 13 Mar 94 p 1 AU1303162694 Vienna KURIER Language: German Article Type:BFN [Unattributed report: "Ex-GDR Interior Minister: Dozens of Stasi Spies in Austria"] [Text] In an exclusive interview for KURIER, Peter-Michael Diestel, former GDR interior minister and Christian Democratic Union [CDU] Landtag deputy in Brandenburg, has confirmed that several Austrians were employed by the Stasi and that they are quite possibly continuing their work for other intelligence services.
